2. Interpretation
In this Act, unless the context otherwise requires—
"Board" means the Botswana Agricultural Marketing Board established under section 3;
"chairman" means the member designated as such by the Minister under section 4(1);
"deputy chairman" means the member designated as such by the Minister under section 4(1);
"development fund" means the development fund established under section 13(1);
"member" means a member of the Board;
"scheduled produce" means the produce specified in the First Schedule;
"stabilisation fund" means the stabilisation fund established under section 12(1).
